       -[ cft.py ]-
 -[ Common Folder Tidy ]-
  

 
 [ About ]

  Welcome here! Common Folder Tidy(CFT) is a simple, useful and powerful tool to help 
  make your Computer(Such as Download folders and Desktop) clean and tidy.
  CFT is written in Python language. Works on Mac, Windows, Linux and other 
  POSIX-compatible platforms.

  CFT requires the following package to run:

  * [python](http://python.org/) â€” we recommend using version 2.7 (the latest is 2.7.5)

  It will be my pleasure if you want to translate CFT instructions and other documents 
  into your language(including English), please let me know :) Any questions, suggestions 
  or bug reports are also welcome, or you can just connecting on CFT Issues.

  This program is free software; you can redistribute it and modify it under the terms
  of the GNU General Public License as published by the Free Software Foundation; 
  either version 3 of the License, or any later version.

  Thank you for you using!


  
 [ Options ]

   Usage: Python cft.py [PATH] 
   
	Advanced Options:
  	 
        -h            	help menu

        -v     		version of the program	

	-f      	search files matching given patterns
			-f [PATH] [FILENAME]

		

 [ Configuration ]

   Common Folder Tidy has configuration file cft.cfg with instructions.



